snippet.textDisplay: Gul Panra just put her hands on her ears at the end lol. She seems overwhelmed throughout the song. I really loved the energy of the song. I have so many memories of Hawa Hawa. It used to play on PTV and we used to hum along while playing. Hassan Jahangir surely hasn't lost his magic, his charm and swag. He enjoyed every second of the song as if he was singing it for the first time. Like many others, I wish it was much longer because I really really loved it.
